      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00002-000-00089"/><hi rend="latintype">Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50"><hi rend="latintype">Wien</hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb168934" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">IX. Franckgasse 1</hi>.</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00002-000-00090"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb197" type="place">Weimar</rs>, <rs ref="#pmb11461" type="person">Gœthe</rs>’s <rs type="place" ref="#pmb193">Gartenhaus</rs>.</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00002-000-00090"/><date>28 VIII.</date></dateline></opener><p>Eine <rs ref="#pmb197" type="place">weimar</rs>i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>che <rs type="person" ref="#pmb40864" subtype="implied">Hofdame</rs>: »Ich intere<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>iere mich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr für
               einen Landsmann von Ihnen, der<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o früh ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>torben i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t und de<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en Werke alle er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t nach<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>einem Tod er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chienen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind: Arthur Schnitzler.« Ich: Ich glaube, Sie irren<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich. Sie:
               O, besti<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>t nicht.</p></div>
      </body>
